  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0 \u0d8b\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0dda \u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddd \u0d91\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Opposition party leaders oppose the use of live ammunition against protesters",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Mano Ganesan, Member of Parliament, said that the opposition party leaders were against giving approval for the use of live bullets against the protestors.",
        "Mr. Mano Ganesan said on his Twitter account that the leaders of Vipakya protested in the party leaders' meeting held yesterday under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena.",
        "He says that the three armed forces commanders and the Inspector General of Police were also present for this party leader meeting."
      ],
